<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>CampuZ Support</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Official support page for CampuZ, the student campus app built for Stony Brook University students." />
  <style>
    :root {
      --red: #990000;
      --red-dark: #6f0000;
      --gray-900: #161616;
      --gray-700: #424242;
      --gray-100: #f5f5f5;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --border: #e6e6e6;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--gray-900);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff 0%, #fafafa 45%, #f4f4f4 100%);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    header {
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #c40000 0%, var(--red) 38%, var(--red-dark) 100%);
      color: var(--white);
      padding: 72px 20px 64px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 7px 14px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(38px, 6vw, 68px);
      line-height: 1;
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    header p {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      font-size: 18px;
      opacity: 0.94;
    }

    main {
      max-width: 1080px;
      margin: -34px auto 64px;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 28px;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    }

    .wide {
      grid-column: span 2;
    }

    .full {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
    }

    h2 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: 26px;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    h3 {
      margin: 22px 0 8px;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    p {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      color: var(--gray-700);
    }

    ul, ol {
      padding-left: 20px;
      color: var(--gray-700);
    }

    li {
      margin: 7px 0;
    }

    a {
      color: var(--red);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 650;
    }

    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .button-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 46px;
      padding: 0 18px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--red);
      color: var(--white);
      font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .button.secondary {
      background: var(--gray-100);
      color: var(--gray-900);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .notice {
      border-left: 4px solid var(--red);
      background: #fff6f6;
      padding: 16px 18px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      margin-top: 16px;
      color: var(--gray-700);
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 32px 20px 52px;
      color: #777;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 820px) {
      .grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .wide, .full {
        grid-column: auto;
      }

      header {
        padding: 56px 20px 52px;
      }

      main {
        margin-top: -24px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="badge">Official CampuZ Support</div>
    <h1>How can we help?</h1>
    <p>
      CampuZ is a student campus app built to help Stony Brook University students access campus tools, chat, bus information, maps, schedules, and beta features in one place.
    </p>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="grid">
      <div class="card wide">
        <h2>Contact Support</h2>
        <p>
          Need help with login, chat, maps, bus tracking, feedback, schedule setup, or a bug in the app? Contact CampuZ support and include your device type, app version, and a short description of the issue.
        </p>
        <p>
          Email: <a href="mailto:thai.tran@stonybrook.edu">thai.tran@stonybrook.edu</a> or <a href="mailto:robert.figueroa@stonybrook.edu">robert.figueroa@stonybrook.edu</a><br />
          Phone: <a href="tel:+12295292445">229-529-2445</a>
        </p>
        <div class="button-row">
          <a class="button" href="mailto:thai.tran@stonybrook.edu,robert.figueroa@stonybrook.edu?subject=CampuZ%20Support%20Request">Email Support</a>
          <a class="button secondary" href="tel:+12295292445">Call Support</a>
        </div>
        <div class="notice">
          Beta note: Some features may still be under development. If something says “to be implemented,” it means the feature is planned but not active yet.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Response Time</h2>
        <p>
          During beta, we try to review support messages as soon as possible. For urgent safety concerns, contact campus emergency services or local authorities directly.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Login Help</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Make sure your email address is entered correctly.</li>
          <li>Check your spam or junk folder for verification emails.</li>
          <li>Restart the app if login appears stuck.</li>
          <li>Contact support if your account still cannot sign in.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Chat & Friends</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Friend requests must be accepted before direct chat is available.</li>
          <li>Notifications may require phone permissions to be enabled.</li>
          <li>If messages do not appear, close and reopen the app.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Maps & Bus</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Campus map data may be updated during beta.</li>
          <li>Bus tracking depends on available campus transportation data.</li>
          <li>Report incorrect building names, locations, or route issues.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card full">
        <h2>Account & Data Requests</h2>
        <p>
          To request account deletion, data deletion, or help with your CampuZ account, email CampuZ support from the same email address used for your CampuZ account.
        </p>
        <ol>
          <li>Open your email app.</li>
          <li>Email <a href="mailto:thai.tran@stonybrook.edu,robert.figueroa@stonybrook.edu?subject=CampuZ%20Account%20Deletion%20Request">thai.tran@stonybrook.edu</a> or <a href="mailto:robert.figueroa@stonybrook.edu?subject=CampuZ%20Account%20Deletion%20Request">robert.figueroa@stonybrook.edu</a>.</li>
          <li>Use the subject line: <strong>CampuZ Account Deletion Request</strong>.</li>
          <li>Include the email address connected to your CampuZ account.</li>
        </ol>
        <p>
          We may ask for confirmation before deleting account-related data to protect your account from unauthorized requests.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card full">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <h3>Is CampuZ officially connected to Stony Brook University?</h3>
        <p>
          CampuZ is an independent student-built app for campus convenience unless otherwise stated in the app or on the official website.
        </p>

        <h3>Why are some features not available yet?</h3>
        <p>
          CampuZ is currently in beta. Features such as advising, tutoring, or school-account-linked services may require additional setup before launch.
        </p>

        <h3>Can I suggest a feature?</h3>
        <p>
          Yes. Send feedback through the app or email support with your suggestion.
        </p>

        <h3>Where can I find the privacy policy?</h3>
        <p>
          Visit the CampuZ Privacy Policy page. If your website already has one, link it here: <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    © 2026 CampuZ. Built for students. Not for emergency use.
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
